flowchart TB
  c1[Capture snapshot] --> m1{Matches baseline?}
  m1 -- Yes --> pass([Test passes])
  m1 -- No --> c2[Capture a second time]
  c2 --> m2{Second capture matches...}
  m2 -- Baseline --> resolved([Transient flake\nauto-resolved, test passes])
  m2 -- First capture --> change([Consistent change\nreported for review])
  m2 -- Neither --> c3[Capture a third time\nwith tracing enabled]
  c3 --> m3{Matches baseline?}
  m3 -- Yes --> resolved2([Flake auto-resolved\ntest passes])
  m3 -- No --> unstable([Labeled Unstable\ntrace attached])
